TSS9011W

RECOVERY FILE HAS WRAPPED AROUND

Reason:

The Top Secret Recovery File is full. Changes to the Security File will be
recorded at the beginning of the File; overwriting current data.

Action:

It is not necessary to back up the recovery file if backups are run daily
before the file wraps. If the recovery file is wrapping more than once a day,
it should be enlarged.
